{"TopicId":217308,"ForumId":198,"TopicTitle":"Going from a Scene that Used Capture Mode and then Going to the KSC Screen Causes the Camera to be looking in the wrong direction.","CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-22T01:45:05Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-22T01:45:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EKSP2 Version: \u003C/strong\u003E0.1.2.0.22258\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOperating System: \u003C/strong\u003EWindows 10\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ECPU\u002BGPU\u002BRAM:\u003C/strong\u003E i9 9900K\u002B3070ti\u002B32GB\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EMods Used: \u003C/strong\u003ENone\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EHow to Test:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLaunch a craft from the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E or load a craft in scene.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nChange to Capture Mode\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nMove Camera in some way\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nGo to the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E Screen\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EThings to Note:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSometimes the incorrect \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E Screen perspective will persist.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSometimes it will face in a different direction but then the camera will attempt to reset to the default \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E perspective a moment later. Sometimes its successful. Sometimes it isn\u0027t.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAt least once the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E Screen inherited the Capture Mode\u0027s Speed.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EScreenshot of One that Persisted:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1039965578754007060/1109990211984834650/image.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-06-01T03:48:32Z\u0022 title=\u002206/01/2023 03:48  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJune 1, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Anth12\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}